snippet.title: Hollowbody - Exclusive Story Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description: Take a look at the latest trailer for the third-person psychological horror game Hollowbody. A dystopian tech-noir survival horror short story that explores themes of identity, perception, and the consequences of one's choices. Hollowbody is launching soon on PC.
